  "short_text": "Sum of Digits",
  "content": "Write a program to print the sum of all the digits in the given number.<hr><b>Input</b><br/><br/>The input will be a single line containing a positive integer.<hr><b>Output</b><br/><br/>The output should be a single line containing the sum of the digits in the given number.<hr><b>Explanation</b><br/><br/>For example, if the given number is 151893, your code should print the sum of all the digits in the given number (1 + 5 + 1 + 8 + 9 + 3), which is 27.<br/><br/>For example, if the given number is 692, your code should print the sum of all the digits in the given number (6 + 9 + 2 ), which is 17.",
